26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bios_cstep.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include <subdev/bios.h>
30#include <subdev/bios/bit.h>
31#include <subdev/bios/cstep.h>
32
33u16
34nvbios_cstepTe(struct nvkm_bios *bios,
35 u8 *ver, u8 *hdr, u8 *cnt, u8 *len, u8 *xnr, u8 *xsz)
36{
37 struct bit_entry bit_P;
38 u16 cstep = 0x0000;
39
40 if (!bit_entry(bios, 'P', &bit_P)) {
41 if (bit_P.version == 2)
42 cstep = nvbios_rd16(bios, bit_P.offset + 0x34);
43
44 if (cstep) {
45 *ver = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 0);
46 switch (*ver) {
47 case 0x10:
48 *hdr = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 1);
49 *cnt = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 3);
50 *len = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 2);
51 *xnr = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 5);
52 *xsz = nvbios_rd08(bios, cstep + 4);
53 return cstep;
54 default:
55 break;
56 }
57 }
58 }
59
60 return 0x0000;
61}
62
63u16
64nvbios_cstepEe(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr)
65{
66 u8 cnt, len, xnr, xsz;
67 u16 data = nvbios_cstepTe(bios, ver, hdr, &cnt, &len, &xnr, &xsz);
68 if (data && idx < cnt) {
69 data = data + *hdr + (idx * len);
70 *hdr = len;
71 return data;
72 }
73 return 0x0000;
74}
75
76u16
77nvbios_cstepEp(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr,
78 struct nvbios_cstepE *info)
79{
80 u16 data = nvbios_cstepEe(bios, idx, ver, hdr);
81 memset(info, 0x00, sizeof(*info));
82 if (data) {
83 info->pstate = (nvbios_rd16(bios, data + 0x00) & 0x01e0) >> 5;
84 info->index = nvbios_rd08(bios, data + 0x03);
85 }
86 return data;
87}
88
89u16
90nvbios_cstepEm(struct nvkm_bios *bios, u8 pstate, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr,
91 struct nvbios_cstepE *info)
92{
93 u32 data, idx = 0;
94 while ((data = nvbios_cstepEp(bios, idx++, ver, hdr, info))) {
95 if (info->pstate == pstate)
96 break;
97 }
98 return data;
99}
100
101u16
102nvbios_cstepXe(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr)
103{
104 u8 cnt, len, xnr, xsz;
105 u16 data = nvbios_cstepTe(bios, ver, hdr, &cnt, &len, &xnr, &xsz);
106 if (data && idx < xnr) {
107 data = data + *hdr + (cnt * len) + (idx * xsz);
108 *hdr = xsz;
109 return data;
110 }
111 return 0x0000;
112}
113
114u16
115nvbios_cstepXp(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr,
116 struct nvbios_cstepX *info)
117{
118 u16 data = nvbios_cstepXe(bios, idx, ver, hdr);
119 memset(info, 0x00, sizeof(*info));
120 if (data) {
121 info->freq = nvbios_rd16(bios, data + 0x00) * 1000;
122 info->unkn[0] = nvbios_rd08(bios, data + 0x02);
123 info->unkn[1] = nvbios_rd08(bios, data + 0x03);
124 info->voltage = nvbios_rd08(bios, data + 0x04);
125 }
126 return data;
127}
